OL,3,CWarning after children dig huge hole
OL,4,Con Cornwall beach
OL,6,FBeachgoers are being warned against
OL,7,Fdigging holes in the sand after a
OL,8,Fgiant ditch appeared on a beach in
OL,9,FCornwall.
OL,11,FPolzeath Beach Ranger Service said it
OL,12,Fwas alerted to the six-foot deep pit
OL,13,Fon 29th August and said that
OL,14,F"thankfully... the walls stayed firm
OL,15,Fenough to prevent a collapse followed
OL,16,Fby suffocation of little people".
OL,18,FThe service is now warning parents not
OL,19,Fto let their children dig deep holes
OL,20,Fon the beach as they can collapse and
OL,21,Fbury those inside.
