OL,3,CWarning after children dig huge hole
OL,4,Con Cornwall beach
OL,6,FIn a post on Facebook, the beach
OL,7,Frangers said: "We are shocked that the
OL,8,Fowners of several children (3-4 feet
OL,9,Ftall) stood by for several hours as
OL,10,Fthey dug this 6ft sand pit.
OL,12,F"The parents weren't thinking straight
OL,13,Fthat day, they left without filling
OL,14,Fthe pit in. It's less than 10m from a
OL,15,Flicensed premises and hidden behind a
OL,16,Fmerch trailer - an area that is cast
OL,17,Finto shadows from flood lighting after
OL,18,Fdark.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
