OL,3,CWarning after children dig huge hole
OL,4,Con Cornwall beach
OL,6,F"Thankfully, the sand didn't dry out,
OL,7,Fand the walls stayed firm enough for
OL,8,Flong enough to prevent a collapse
OL,9,Ffollowed by crushing and/or
OL,10,Fsuffocation of the little people."
OL,12,FThe service said that a member of the
OL,13,Fpublic let them know about the hole
OL,14,Fand helped fill it in.
OL,16,FPolzeath Coastguard and Wadebridge
OL,17,FCommunity Fire Station routinely
OL,18,Fpractice sand pit rescues.
